					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Background: After <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/silent-forest-ikuragunkan">Silent Forest</a> (or you can simply read it as an independent fanart):</p> <p>SF girl and 2521 lived happily ever after → passed away → many years later → 2521 couldn't forget SF girl → “The same eyes, lonely, but desired to be loved” → &quot;I fancy you…r eyes.&quot;</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Some&nbsp;notes</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>1-[deleted]<br /> 2-Thank you to whoever helped me with listpages problems, special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/feitag" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4357011&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555556940" alt="feitag" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4357011)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/feitag" >feitag</a></span> on coding things<br /> 3-And <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1500566&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555556940" alt="LurkD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1500566)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" >LurkD</a></span> &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ikuragunkan" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2246445&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555556940" alt="ikuragunkan" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2246445)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ikuragunkan" >ikuragunkan</a></span>, love your work :D<br /> 4-How can I put the image on last page (<em>you have her eyes</em>) in the middle?<br /> 5-Not sure if I should add &quot;international&quot; tag here since I'm the author, but please add it if needed.<br /> 5-1st time draw something with contents, trying the same storyboard/onomatopoeia/etc with SF.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Hope you enjoy</p> 
